    <item>
      <title>日本官员努力在市场震荡后恢复平静</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/japan-s-mimura-says-government-boj-will-keep-working-closely</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股市出现 30 多年来最大跌幅，引发对货币政策紧缩的批评，给鼓励家庭投资资产的努力蒙上阴影。此后，日本政府和央行试图展现统一战线，恢复金融市场的平静。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/japan-s-mimura-says-government-boj-will-keep-working-closely</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 07:32:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非城镇欠水务局 12 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/south-african-towns-owe-water-boards-1-2-billion-bus-day-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《商业日报》援引水利与卫生部长佩米·马约迪纳的话称，南非 15 个水务局共欠下各市政府 213 亿兰特（12 亿美元）的债务，这些债务威胁到这些水务局的财务生存能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/south-african-towns-owe-water-boards-1-2-billion-bus-day-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 07:00:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰晤士水务公司寻求协议逃避 1.04 亿英镑污水处理罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/thames-water-fined-04-million-for-sewage-spills-in-new-setback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[资金短缺的泰晤士水务公司正寻求与其监管机构达成协议，以避免因污染河流而被罚款 1.04 亿英镑（1.33 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/thames-water-fined-04-million-for-sewage-spills-in-new-setback</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 06:10:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯赢得提名，巩固与特朗普的对决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/harris-clinches-democratic-nomination-cementing-trump-matchup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 获得民主党总统候选人提名，在一场网络唱名投票中获胜，成为第一位领导美国主要政党总统候选人的黑人女性和亚裔美国人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/harris-clinches-democratic-nomination-cementing-trump-matchup</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 03:50:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国解散议会，为新政府铺平道路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/bangladesh-president-vows-to-hold-election-as-soon-as-possible</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国于周二解散了国家议会，为长期领导人谢赫哈西娜下台后组建军方支持的临时政府和举行新的选举铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/bangladesh-president-vows-to-hold-election-as-soon-as-possible</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 00:56:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国财政部长里夫斯拒绝排除提高资本利得税的可能性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/uk-s-reeves-declines-to-rule-out-increase-in-capital-gains-tax</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 拒绝排除增加资本利得税的可能性，并警告说将做出艰难的决定来填补 220 亿英镑（280 亿美元）的预算黑洞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/uk-s-reeves-declines-to-rule-out-increase-in-capital-gains-tax</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 22:45:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国骚乱：南港谋杀案后为何爆发暴力事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/uk-far-right-riots-why-violence-erupted-after-southport-murders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国遭遇了十多年来最严重的骚乱，最初是由英格兰西北部三名女孩被谋杀而引发的，随后演变成全国城镇的反移民和种族主义暴力事件。英国首相凯尔·斯塔默表示，暴乱者将面临“法律的全面制裁”，但这场骚乱凸显出，工党在选举中取得压倒性胜利掩盖了极端政治边缘势力试图利用的深刻分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/uk-far-right-riots-why-violence-erupted-after-southport-murders</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 14:20:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
